--de_coldstorm_rc1--

Coldstorm is a bomb/defuse map created by J4CK8 and Mikeypilk. Rc1 features numerous bug fixes and some extra detailing.
Included is:
A custom nav (Mostly works-ish)
A custom radar
Custom textures
Some special music
3d skybox

Thanks to TopHATTwaffle for most of the custom textures in the map.

Visit http://jammyleveldesign.blogspot.com to see more of our levels and development info.
